init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The world is about to change again, and the only question is whether it will be for the better, or for the worse.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The story is told through the eyes of the main character, a young man named David, who is the son of a powerful mage.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: David is a "Mana Sensitive", meaning he can sense the presence of mana in the world around him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This ability is very rare, and is the reason that David is constantly being hunted by the aliens.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The story begins with David's father, a powerful mage, being killed by the aliens.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: David is then forced to flee from the aliens, and he soon meets up with a group of other people who are also Mana Sensitives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Together, they form a resistance against the aliens, and try to find a way to defeat them.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens are a threat to the mana sensitive, but also to the entire world.
